1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:30,520 --> 00:01:34,940
[Mysterious Lotus Casebook]

3
00:01:41,009 --> 00:01:43,080
[Episode 10]

4
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:46,320
Physician Li,

5
00:01:47,110 --> 00:01:49,830
I've been thinking about a small question.

6
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:54,370
Why don't you reveal your face?

7
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:01,680
Master Bai.

8
00:02:02,430 --> 00:02:03,470
Here's the thing.

9
00:02:04,020 --> 00:02:07,020
I'm just a physician who wanders in the martial arts world.

10
00:02:07,020 --> 00:02:08,350
I'm rootless.

11
00:02:08,660 --> 00:02:11,410
It's also my duty to cure people and save people's lives.

12
00:02:11,410 --> 00:02:12,090
Besides,

13
00:02:12,660 --> 00:02:13,990
when I cure good people,

14
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:15,759
bad people want to kill me.

15
00:02:15,810 --> 00:02:17,090
When I cure bad people,

16
00:02:17,430 --> 00:02:18,890
good people are not happy.

17
00:02:19,070 --> 00:02:21,540
There are so many people in the Sword-Appreciation Ceremony.

18
00:02:21,540 --> 00:02:23,420
There are also many enemies.

19
00:02:23,730 --> 00:02:24,990
It's not too much for me

20
00:02:25,390 --> 00:02:26,790
to wear this mask, right?

21
00:02:28,760 --> 00:02:29,560
Physician Li.

22
00:02:30,660 --> 00:02:31,540
But why

23
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:34,720
do I seem to have seen you somewhere before?

24
00:02:37,700 --> 00:02:38,770
You've seen me before?

25
00:02:38,770 --> 00:02:39,300
Yes.

26
00:02:41,730 --> 00:02:42,740
Could it be

27
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:46,329
that you've seen my elder brother before?

28
00:02:46,430 --> 00:02:47,560
Your elder brother?

29
00:02:49,260 --> 00:02:51,790
Have you really seen my elder brother before?

30
00:02:52,980 --> 00:02:54,240
I'm sorry, Master Yun.

31
00:02:55,250 --> 00:02:55,850
Yes.

32
00:02:56,780 --> 00:02:59,670
I do have a twin brother.

33
00:03:00,060 --> 00:03:01,060
My mother named us

34
00:03:01,410 --> 00:03:02,450
Li Lianpeng

35
00:03:02,610 --> 00:03:04,150
and Li Lianhua respectively.

36
00:03:04,150 --> 00:03:06,260
-Li Lianpeng.
-Lianpeng is my elder brother.

37
00:03:06,260 --> 00:03:08,050
I'm the younger brother.

38
00:03:08,310 --> 00:03:10,460
We were born in a poor family.

39
00:03:12,020 --> 00:03:14,960
Soon after my brother was born,

40
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:17,700
he was taken away by an old man

41
00:03:18,370 --> 00:03:19,430
as his adopted son.

42
00:03:20,310 --> 00:03:23,230
Since then, I've never seen him again.

43
00:03:24,060 --> 00:03:25,110
But I also heard

44
00:03:26,260 --> 00:03:28,550
that my brother is quite awesome.

45
00:03:29,210 --> 00:03:30,300
So in this world,

46
00:03:31,190 --> 00:03:33,310
there is a person who resembles me.

47
00:03:35,820 --> 00:03:37,780
Li Lianpeng?

48
00:03:37,900 --> 00:03:40,020
It's true. I never lie.

49
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:47,270
Physician Li.

50
00:03:47,770 --> 00:03:48,920
Your family is poor,

51
00:03:49,540 --> 00:03:52,210
but the Lotus Tower has a unique structure

52
00:03:52,300 --> 00:03:53,540
and shows exquisite craftsmanship.

53
00:03:53,540 --> 00:03:54,400
It's valuable.

54
00:03:55,030 --> 00:03:56,160
Where did you get it?

55
00:04:00,990 --> 00:04:03,050
A few years ago, I saw a big shabby boat

56
00:04:03,170 --> 00:04:05,130
floating on the sea.

57
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,570
No one had interest in it.

58
00:04:08,070 --> 00:04:10,130
So I picked up the wood

59
00:04:10,670 --> 00:04:12,310
and made it into a Lotus Tower.

60
00:04:12,310 --> 00:04:14,790
You can ask the fishermen about it by the sea.

61
00:04:15,300 --> 00:04:16,430
I didn't steal it.

62
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:22,370
Physician Li, what are you talking about?

63
00:04:22,649 --> 00:04:24,970
Biqiu just asked casually.

64
00:04:27,829 --> 00:04:28,490
Pingchuan.

65
00:04:31,370 --> 00:04:32,700
I was reckless just now.

66
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,550
I guess

67
00:04:34,890 --> 00:04:37,100
you haven't eaten anything since last night.

68
00:04:37,100 --> 00:04:38,480
This is the peanut porridge

69
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:41,090
I specially asked someone to buy from Zuijiang Restaurant.

70
00:04:41,090 --> 00:04:41,890
Physician Li.

71
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:42,510
Try it.

72
00:04:44,650 --> 00:04:45,909
Thank you, Master Yun.

73
00:04:46,490 --> 00:04:47,750
Sir, put it here.

74
00:04:47,780 --> 00:04:48,909
I'll drink it later.

75
00:04:51,420 --> 00:04:53,280
If the peanut porridge gets cold,

76
00:04:53,780 --> 00:04:55,760
then my kindness is for nothing.

77
00:04:56,380 --> 00:04:57,710
Drink it while it's hot.

78
00:05:01,140 --> 00:05:03,180
Thank you.

79
00:05:04,740 --> 00:05:05,610
It smells good.

80
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,750
It looks good.

81
00:05:14,330 --> 00:05:16,110
Why are there peanuts in the porridge?

82
00:05:16,110 --> 00:05:17,170
Why can't there be?

83
00:05:17,260 --> 00:05:19,190
Xiangyi has an allergy to peanuts.

84
00:05:20,270 --> 00:05:20,730
This...

85
00:05:22,510 --> 00:05:24,440
I have an allergic reaction again.

86
00:05:34,850 --> 00:05:37,190
Since you've been poisoned with the deadliest poison,

87
00:05:37,190 --> 00:05:40,010
no poison can harm you anymore.

88
00:05:41,530 --> 00:05:42,330
Physician Li.

89
00:05:42,850 --> 00:05:44,110
You still need to rest.

90
00:05:44,390 --> 00:05:45,830
We won't disturb you then.

91
00:05:45,830 --> 00:05:46,740
I've had enough porridge.

92
00:05:46,740 --> 00:05:47,340
Thank you.

93
00:05:47,900 --> 00:05:48,960
I won't see you off.

94
00:05:50,710 --> 00:05:51,240
Let's go.

95
00:06:01,430 --> 00:06:02,110
Li Lianhua.

96
00:06:05,659 --> 00:06:09,550
Someone poisoned his friend who he respected most

97
00:06:10,820 --> 00:06:12,990
for a woman

98
00:06:13,700 --> 00:06:16,700
and caused his friend to fall into the East Sea and die.

99
00:06:16,850 --> 00:06:17,620
Do you think

100
00:06:19,260 --> 00:06:20,860
this person deserves to die?

101
00:06:22,990 --> 00:06:24,870
Yes. He indeed deserves to die.

102
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:30,440
Did this person have intention to kill his friend?

103
00:06:32,660 --> 00:06:33,700
That woman said

104
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:38,450
she didn't want Li Xiangyi to appear in the East Seaside.

105
00:06:38,670 --> 00:06:41,530
She didn't allow Di Feisheng to be killed by others.

106
00:06:41,960 --> 00:06:44,980
But Sect Leader's martial art skills are unpredictable.

107
00:06:44,980 --> 00:06:47,490
If I hadn't poisoned him with the deadliest poison,

108
00:06:47,490 --> 00:06:49,090
I couldn't have stopped him.

109
00:06:49,770 --> 00:06:52,780
I thought I only needed to stop him for a while.

110
00:06:54,140 --> 00:06:55,650
I had the antidote anyway.

111
00:06:56,500 --> 00:06:58,030
I thought it didn't matter.

112
00:06:58,420 --> 00:07:00,080
But things weren't like that.

113
00:07:01,060 --> 00:07:02,440
The antidote is fake.

114
00:07:03,380 --> 00:07:07,800
All the things happened because I was too stupid.

115
00:07:09,490 --> 00:07:11,290
Even if I didn't want to kill him,

116
00:07:13,420 --> 00:07:14,840
I did kill him.

117
00:07:16,950 --> 00:07:18,280
If you were Sect Leader,

118
00:07:19,570 --> 00:07:21,570
you would hate me to the core, right?

119
00:07:22,260 --> 00:07:23,520
If I were him,

120
00:07:24,860 --> 00:07:26,460
I would definitely hate you.

121
00:07:29,300 --> 00:07:30,360
But think about it.

122
00:07:30,610 --> 00:07:32,120
You said he has died.

123
00:07:32,780 --> 00:07:35,170
Why would the dead hate you?

124
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:36,740
Besides,

125
00:07:37,260 --> 00:07:39,870
all grudges are gone.

126
00:07:40,610 --> 00:07:42,110
They've become the past.

127
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:44,650
I think you should forget it.

128
00:07:47,590 --> 00:07:49,050
Should I really forget it?

129
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:52,590
How is it?

130
00:07:53,630 --> 00:07:54,590
We've tested it.

131
00:07:54,790 --> 00:07:55,870
He's not him at all.

132
00:08:03,860 --> 00:08:06,690
He's really not him.

133
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,370
Mr. Li.

134
00:08:15,180 --> 00:08:15,730
Ms. Qiao.

135
00:08:21,020 --> 00:08:23,970
Last time, you asked me to investigate the whereabouts of Shi Hun.

136
00:08:23,970 --> 00:08:25,120
I found some clues.

137
00:08:25,370 --> 00:08:27,100
[To Qiao Wanmian. May 28, the year of Renyin.]

138
00:08:26,070 --> 00:08:27,800
When we let him go ten years ago,

139
00:08:28,070 --> 00:08:29,820
he wrote a letter to thank us.

140
00:08:30,270 --> 00:08:32,990
It was sent from Cailian Manor in Xueyu Town.

141
00:08:33,880 --> 00:08:35,600
But it happened ten years ago.

142
00:08:36,020 --> 00:08:37,400
There is a sea of faces in the world.

143
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:39,590
It's not easy to get some clues.

144
00:08:39,900 --> 00:08:41,030
Thank you, Ms. Qiao.

145
00:08:41,220 --> 00:08:42,549
You're welcome, Mr. Li.

146
00:08:43,220 --> 00:08:46,230
Actually, I'm here today also for another thing.

147
00:08:46,990 --> 00:08:47,919
Say it, Ms. Qiao.

148
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:54,000
The sachet...

149
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,880
You reminded me.

150
00:08:59,640 --> 00:09:01,940
Mr. Xiao took you away in a hurry yesterday.

151
00:09:01,940 --> 00:09:03,100
I kept it.

152
00:09:03,460 --> 00:09:05,750
It belonged to your deceased friend.

153
00:09:05,850 --> 00:09:07,250
I should return it to you.

154
00:09:13,820 --> 00:09:14,350
Ms. Qiao.

155
00:09:19,700 --> 00:09:23,860
I made this sachet for him.

156
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,370
It's been ten years.

157
00:09:28,020 --> 00:09:29,250
I've held out hope

158
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:33,650
for ten years.

159
00:09:42,180 --> 00:09:44,180
Although I thought about it before,

160
00:09:46,700 --> 00:09:48,560
the fact that he doesn't come back

161
00:09:49,540 --> 00:09:50,490
is the answer.

162
00:09:56,850 --> 00:09:57,530
Although

163
00:10:00,910 --> 00:10:02,630
I'm mentally prepared,

164
00:10:03,750 --> 00:10:04,590
when

165
00:10:05,890 --> 00:10:07,730
I heard he is dead,

166
00:10:08,690 --> 00:10:09,380
I still...

167
00:10:12,780 --> 00:10:13,700
I still...

168
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:14,330
Ms. Qiao.

169
00:10:16,130 --> 00:10:17,590
He's already passed away.

170
00:10:18,410 --> 00:10:21,080
Don't be too sad.

171
00:10:25,860 --> 00:10:26,500
Mr. Li.

172
00:10:30,110 --> 00:10:30,640
I...

173
00:10:37,790 --> 00:10:39,360
I once had

174
00:10:42,570 --> 00:10:44,520
some ridiculous thoughts.

175
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:57,280
It was just because I couldn't accept the reality.

176
00:10:57,530 --> 00:10:58,770
I deceived myself.

177
00:10:59,780 --> 00:11:00,470
Now,

178
00:11:01,940 --> 00:11:03,200
I should clear my mind.

179
00:11:07,140 --> 00:11:08,630
This is his personal item.

180
00:11:12,940 --> 00:11:14,600
It's good to let it go with him.

181
00:11:27,770 --> 00:11:32,110
The ten-year wait has ended.

182
00:11:47,350 --> 00:11:49,210
Since he's your deceased friend,

183
00:11:49,260 --> 00:11:50,660
let him stay in the story.

184
00:11:52,350 --> 00:11:55,390
Ms. Qiao, you should move on without worries.

185
00:11:57,380 --> 00:11:58,020
Mr. Li.

186
00:11:58,720 --> 00:11:59,510
Thank you.

187
00:12:13,930 --> 00:12:14,480
Ms. Qiao.

188
00:12:20,250 --> 00:12:21,980
Why did Ms. Qiao also come here?

189
00:12:24,570 --> 00:12:25,570
Let me remind you.

190
00:12:25,820 --> 00:12:27,740
Ms. Qiao is already spoken for.

191
00:12:27,970 --> 00:12:29,430
Don't have designs on her.

192
00:12:31,540 --> 00:12:33,110
I heard from the little monks in the courtyard

193
00:12:33,110 --> 00:12:36,440
that all the masters of the Baichuan Court came here before.

194
00:12:37,460 --> 00:12:38,990
You didn't come at that time.

195
00:12:38,990 --> 00:12:39,990
Do you know

196
00:12:40,930 --> 00:12:42,390
what Master Ji brought me?

197
00:12:43,510 --> 00:12:44,440
Shaoshi Sword.

198
00:12:44,780 --> 00:12:45,640
Shaoshi Sword?

199
00:12:46,830 --> 00:12:47,760
Did you touch it?

200
00:12:47,900 --> 00:12:48,890
Of course.

201
00:12:49,650 --> 00:12:50,540
To be honest,

202
00:12:51,450 --> 00:12:53,110
I saved Ms. Qiao in the tunnel.

203
00:12:53,860 --> 00:12:54,920
In order to thank me,

204
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:56,070
they let me have a look

205
00:12:56,070 --> 00:12:57,310
and touch it.

206
00:12:57,890 --> 00:12:58,750
Let me tell you.

207
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,530
This sword is really heavy.

208
00:13:00,710 --> 00:13:01,960
My hand hurt when I touched it.

209
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:03,580
I couldn't lift it immediately.

210
00:13:03,580 --> 00:13:05,440
You're so lucky.

211
00:13:05,660 --> 00:13:06,870
I can't even touch it.

212
00:13:08,410 --> 00:13:08,900
Look.

213
00:13:09,210 --> 00:13:10,510
My hand became callused after I touched it.

214
00:13:10,510 --> 00:13:11,200
Cut it out.

215
00:13:11,950 --> 00:13:12,830
How rude of you!

216
00:13:12,870 --> 00:13:14,500
You've taken your medicine?

217
00:13:14,910 --> 00:13:16,040
I've told Bhante Wuliao.

218
00:13:16,040 --> 00:13:17,440
He'll check on you later.

219
00:13:19,060 --> 00:13:19,650
Thanks.

220
00:13:33,380 --> 00:13:35,220
How long do you think your life

221
00:13:35,220 --> 00:13:36,880
will let you suffer like this?

222
00:13:37,030 --> 00:13:38,560
I've warned you many times.

223
00:13:39,190 --> 00:13:41,590
You have the unique Yangzhouman.

224
00:13:41,980 --> 00:13:42,820
That's why you still have

225
00:13:42,820 --> 00:13:45,650
ten percent of the internal power which can protect your heart.

226
00:13:45,650 --> 00:13:48,430
Every time you use it, the effect of the poison accelerates.

227
00:13:48,430 --> 00:13:49,910
Why don't you listen?

228
00:13:50,770 --> 00:13:53,920
Bicha Poison will affect your brain.

229
00:13:54,210 --> 00:13:55,470
You're a smart person.

230
00:13:55,780 --> 00:13:58,040
If you suddenly become crazy and stupid,

231
00:13:58,790 --> 00:14:00,940
I... I won't be used to it.

232
00:14:01,770 --> 00:14:03,080
You have to get used to it.

233
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:04,220
Old Monk, stop talking.

234
00:14:04,220 --> 00:14:05,550
If you continue to talk,

235
00:14:05,910 --> 00:14:06,820
I will have a headache

236
00:14:06,820 --> 00:14:08,350
and won't hear you clearly.

237
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:09,480
Don't interrupt.

238
00:14:10,700 --> 00:14:12,960
If you continue to use Genuine Qi at will,

239
00:14:13,180 --> 00:14:15,780
I'm afraid you'll only have six months to live.

240
00:14:16,050 --> 00:14:17,530
It's fine.

241
00:14:17,970 --> 00:14:19,130
When she was in trouble,

242
00:14:19,130 --> 00:14:21,460
I couldn't just stand by and watch her die.

243
00:14:21,820 --> 00:14:23,680
Is it because you couldn't stand by and watch her die

244
00:14:23,680 --> 00:14:26,610
or you still have feelings for Ms. Qiao?

245
00:14:28,230 --> 00:14:30,120
Old Monk, don't talk nonsense.

246
00:14:30,390 --> 00:14:31,470
Mian is the only one

247
00:14:31,500 --> 00:14:33,770
who can offer me clues to find the corpse of my senior.

248
00:14:33,770 --> 00:14:35,230
Of course I care about her.

249
00:14:36,340 --> 00:14:37,930
People go to heaven when they die.

250
00:14:37,930 --> 00:14:40,060
Why do you insist

251
00:14:40,510 --> 00:14:42,370
on finding the corpse of Mr. Shan?

252
00:14:42,460 --> 00:14:43,790
Why don't you come back?

253
00:14:47,340 --> 00:14:48,710
You've met Yun Biqiu.

254
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:52,330
I know you don't mind

255
00:14:52,420 --> 00:14:54,700
that he was bewitched by Jiao Liqiao

256
00:14:55,180 --> 00:14:57,180
and poisoned you with Bicha Poison.

257
00:14:58,230 --> 00:14:59,260
Bicha Poison?

258
00:15:02,640 --> 00:15:03,550
I won.

259
00:15:05,750 --> 00:15:09,270
Ten years ago, Di Feisheng wanted to battle with you.

260
00:15:10,270 --> 00:15:11,850
But he didn't expect

261
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:13,510
the one he won in the end

262
00:15:14,020 --> 00:15:16,220
was poisoned with a deadly poison.

263
00:15:17,530 --> 00:15:18,050
Since

264
00:15:18,050 --> 00:15:20,850
you don't mind that he helped Di Feisheng harm you,

265
00:15:21,940 --> 00:15:23,270
why don't you come back?

266
00:15:23,540 --> 00:15:26,070
If you don't want to say it, I'll say it for you.

267
00:15:26,750 --> 00:15:29,340
You always think it was because you acted willfully

268
00:15:29,340 --> 00:15:30,940
and declared war on the Jinyuan Alliance

269
00:15:30,940 --> 00:15:32,020
that

270
00:15:32,040 --> 00:15:35,250
the 58 heroes of the Sigu Sect died tragically

271
00:15:35,270 --> 00:15:37,640
and that the Sigu Sect split.

272
00:15:40,150 --> 00:15:42,350
It's not that you can't forgive others.

273
00:15:43,570 --> 00:15:45,900
It's that you refuse to forgive yourself.

274
00:15:46,350 --> 00:15:47,080
Are you done?

275
00:15:47,820 --> 00:15:49,880
If you're done, let me say something.

276
00:15:50,830 --> 00:15:51,510
Old Monk.

277
00:15:52,030 --> 00:15:54,490
When did you become an old storyteller monk?

278
00:15:55,160 --> 00:15:56,000
I just think

279
00:15:56,030 --> 00:15:58,510
being Li Xiangyi is too tiring.

280
00:15:59,020 --> 00:16:00,680
Isn't it good to be Li Lianhua?

281
00:16:00,860 --> 00:16:02,190
I can drink tea with you.

282
00:16:03,060 --> 00:16:03,930
Stop it.

283
00:16:04,800 --> 00:16:05,970
It's time for you

284
00:16:06,340 --> 00:16:08,510
to give lessons to the little monks.

285
00:16:08,750 --> 00:16:09,990
Why are you still sitting here?

286
00:16:09,990 --> 00:16:12,990
Otherwise, those little monks will raise the roof again.

287
00:16:12,990 --> 00:16:13,910
Hurry up and go.

288
00:16:34,760 --> 00:16:35,510
Li Xiangyi!

289
00:16:36,270 --> 00:16:37,020
Li Xiangyi.

290
00:16:38,040 --> 00:16:39,100
What are you doing?

291
00:16:39,150 --> 00:16:39,620
Ten years ago,

292
00:16:39,620 --> 00:16:41,540
you lost to me because you were poisoned.

293
00:16:41,540 --> 00:16:42,400
Let me tell you.

294
00:16:42,700 --> 00:16:45,280
Eavesdropping is not a good habit.

295
00:16:49,050 --> 00:16:50,110
What are you doing?

296
00:16:50,210 --> 00:16:52,540
In the battle at the East Sea ten years ago,

297
00:16:52,770 --> 00:16:54,440
I thought I was the world number one

298
00:16:54,440 --> 00:16:56,170
because I won a narrow victory.

299
00:16:56,470 --> 00:16:59,630
Today I heard that I won in an unfair way.

300
00:17:00,040 --> 00:17:02,570
You mean you didn't know anything about this?

301
00:17:04,260 --> 00:17:05,460
Are you insulting me?

302
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:09,800
I see.

303
00:17:10,970 --> 00:17:11,569
Forget it.

304
00:17:11,990 --> 00:17:13,319
Let bygones be bygones.

305
00:17:13,589 --> 00:17:14,940
It doesn't matter who won or lost.

306
00:17:14,940 --> 00:17:15,599
It matters.

307
00:17:16,900 --> 00:17:18,910
I treated you as a worthy opponent.

308
00:17:20,030 --> 00:17:21,680
You made me a joke.

309
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:24,650
Director Di.

310
00:17:25,130 --> 00:17:26,480
It's been so long.

311
00:17:26,579 --> 00:17:29,480
Just pretend that you didn't hear it, okay?

312
00:17:30,020 --> 00:17:30,660
No.

313
00:17:31,280 --> 00:17:33,079
I want to compete with you again.

314
00:17:33,540 --> 00:17:35,480
Let's compete in a fair way.

315
00:17:35,870 --> 00:17:38,670
The problem is that I can't compete with you again.

316
00:17:38,920 --> 00:17:40,130
You know that.

317
00:17:41,370 --> 00:17:43,220
Since you've eavesdropped.

318
00:17:44,340 --> 00:17:44,840
Now,

319
00:17:45,160 --> 00:17:47,170
the poison has entered my bone marrow.

320
00:17:47,170 --> 00:17:49,140
I only have ten percent of my inner power.

321
00:17:49,140 --> 00:17:51,800
Why don't you take a look at the new ranking list?

322
00:17:52,080 --> 00:17:54,640
I heard Buddhist San Sheng is quite awesome.

323
00:17:55,160 --> 00:17:56,560
Go and compete with them.

324
00:17:56,650 --> 00:17:59,570
I have only one opponent in my life.

325
00:18:00,360 --> 00:18:01,430
That is Li Xiangyi.

326
00:18:02,600 --> 00:18:04,260
I only have one wish in my life.

327
00:18:04,780 --> 00:18:05,840
That is to beat him.

328
00:18:05,860 --> 00:18:06,790
I'm sorry.

329
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:08,080
I can't help you.

330
00:18:08,790 --> 00:18:09,600
Now,

331
00:18:09,820 --> 00:18:11,420
you're the world number one.

332
00:18:15,830 --> 00:18:17,460
I don't need you to let me win.

333
00:18:18,130 --> 00:18:19,460
It's just Bicha Poison.

334
00:18:19,940 --> 00:18:21,400
I'll find a way to cure you.

335
00:18:22,860 --> 00:18:24,030
I heard the poison

336
00:18:24,500 --> 00:18:26,230
was created by Medicine Demon.

337
00:18:26,400 --> 00:18:28,400
No one can detoxify it in this world.

338
00:18:28,660 --> 00:18:31,860
Besides, Bhante Wuliao has excellent medical skills.

339
00:18:32,130 --> 00:18:34,560
He hasn't cured me during these ten years.

340
00:18:34,820 --> 00:18:37,380
It doesn't mean I can't cure you.

341
00:18:38,020 --> 00:18:39,820
Tell me the Mantra of Inner Body Cleansing.

342
00:18:39,820 --> 00:18:41,210
I'll find a way to save you.

343
00:18:41,210 --> 00:18:42,540
Do you think I'm stupid?

344
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:44,830
The Mantra of Inner Body Cleansing.

345
00:18:45,320 --> 00:18:46,120
It's easy.

346
00:18:46,910 --> 00:18:49,240
If you help me find the corpse of my senior,

347
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:50,440
I'll tell it to you.

348
00:18:50,440 --> 00:18:52,860
Otherwise, there will be nothing to be discussed.

349
00:18:52,860 --> 00:18:56,260
The corpse of your senior, Shan Gudao,

350
00:18:57,030 --> 00:18:58,590
has long become soil.

351
00:18:58,800 --> 00:19:00,400
Even if it has become soil,

352
00:19:01,220 --> 00:19:02,820
according to our agreement,

353
00:19:03,610 --> 00:19:04,410
if you have it,

354
00:19:05,150 --> 00:19:06,210
I'll swap with you.

355
00:19:06,610 --> 00:19:09,610
If you don't have it, I don't have what you want either.

356
00:19:12,080 --> 00:19:14,010
Are you really not afraid of death?

357
00:19:14,780 --> 00:19:17,130
I already died ten years ago.

358
00:19:17,260 --> 00:19:18,860
Then I'll kill Qiao Wanmian.

359
00:19:18,900 --> 00:19:19,980
Bullying the weak

360
00:19:20,150 --> 00:19:21,390
is more unjust, isn't it?

361
00:19:21,390 --> 00:19:22,800
Then I'll wipe out the Baichuan Court.

362
00:19:22,800 --> 00:19:26,330
Even if you wipe out the whole world, it has nothing to do with me.

363
00:19:27,170 --> 00:19:28,370
Let go of him!

364
00:19:28,440 --> 00:19:30,020
Don't you know he's in poor health?

365
00:19:30,020 --> 00:19:31,260
He even doesn't care about his life.

366
00:19:31,260 --> 00:19:32,190
What do you care about?

367
00:19:32,190 --> 00:19:33,250
Listen carefully.

368
00:19:33,590 --> 00:19:35,150
I don't care what happened between you two.

369
00:19:35,150 --> 00:19:36,740
A gentleman uses words but not his fists.

370
00:19:36,740 --> 00:19:39,140
I won't go easy on you if you keep doing this.

371
00:19:41,860 --> 00:19:44,460
I don't believe you don't care about anything.

372
00:19:51,130 --> 00:19:52,340
Jiao Liqiao.

373
00:20:00,450 --> 00:20:01,170
Hey,

374
00:20:01,740 --> 00:20:03,670
what happened between you and Fei?

375
00:20:04,510 --> 00:20:05,880
There's a misunderstanding.

376
00:20:05,880 --> 00:20:06,370
Go on.

377
00:20:06,750 --> 00:20:07,750
Keep making it up.

378
00:20:08,180 --> 00:20:09,860
I'd like to see what kind of misunderstanding

379
00:20:09,860 --> 00:20:12,060
caused him to almost choke you to death.

380
00:20:12,580 --> 00:20:13,820
If you keep talking,

381
00:20:14,350 --> 00:20:15,650
I'll feel dizzy.

382
00:20:19,770 --> 00:20:20,360
Enough.

383
00:20:21,040 --> 00:20:22,370
I just want to remind you

384
00:20:22,550 --> 00:20:24,150
although Fei is not skilled in martial arts,

385
00:20:24,150 --> 00:20:25,670
he's ruthless when he fights.

386
00:20:25,670 --> 00:20:27,980
You can't let this kind of person stay by your side.

387
00:20:27,980 --> 00:20:29,910
Maybe one day when I'm not with you,

388
00:20:29,980 --> 00:20:31,380
he'll choke you to death.

389
00:20:32,250 --> 00:20:33,690
Pour me some water.

390
00:20:34,210 --> 00:20:35,340
My hands feel weak.

391
00:20:39,060 --> 00:20:39,920
Think about it.

392
00:20:40,190 --> 00:20:41,280
Fei

393
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:42,460
is indeed weired,

394
00:20:42,980 --> 00:20:43,650
but

395
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:45,640
he doesn't want me to die either.

396
00:20:45,640 --> 00:20:46,750
As you saw before,

397
00:20:46,900 --> 00:20:49,010
he's crazy and flaky.

398
00:20:49,120 --> 00:20:50,930
He's a bit out of his mind.

399
00:20:51,620 --> 00:20:53,860
Besides, I have you.

400
00:20:55,670 --> 00:20:56,270
By the way,

401
00:20:56,700 --> 00:20:59,470
I asked you to investigate Cailian Manor in the Baichuan Court yesterday.

402
00:20:59,470 --> 00:21:00,730
Did you find anything?

403
00:21:00,860 --> 00:21:01,710
You don't tell me

404
00:21:01,710 --> 00:21:03,310
what you're thinking about.

405
00:21:03,500 --> 00:21:05,230
But you ask me to do many things.

406
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:10,230
There really were murder cases in Cailian Manor.

407
00:21:15,120 --> 00:21:17,600
[Baichuan Court's Casebook]

408
00:21:15,120 --> 00:21:17,600
[Wedding Dress Murder Cases in Cailian Manor]

409
00:21:17,900 --> 00:21:19,500
Wedding Dress Murder Cases.

410
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:23,680
Three wedding ceremonies have been held in Cailian Manor during these ten years.

411
00:21:21,590 --> 00:21:24,600
[Cailian Manor]

412
00:21:24,200 --> 00:21:25,370
Three brides died.

413
00:21:26,180 --> 00:21:26,950
Strangely,

414
00:21:27,640 --> 00:21:29,790
it happened at intervals of a few years.

415
00:21:29,790 --> 00:21:31,520
But when the three brides died,

416
00:21:31,530 --> 00:21:33,390
they wore the same wedding dress.

417
00:21:34,460 --> 00:21:36,730
It's said that the source of the wedding dress is unknown.

418
00:21:36,730 --> 00:21:38,160
There's resentment on it.

419
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:40,790
Everyone who wears it will suffer misfortune.

420
00:21:44,620 --> 00:21:46,120
It's horrible.

421
00:21:46,820 --> 00:21:48,080
After all these years,

422
00:21:49,410 --> 00:21:51,040
haven't they found any clues to the identities

423
00:21:51,040 --> 00:21:53,040
of the murderers of the three cases?

424
00:21:54,090 --> 00:21:56,140
They were all considered as accidents.

425
00:21:56,140 --> 00:21:56,780
Maybe

426
00:21:57,510 --> 00:21:59,860
they were really caused by the wedding dress.

427
00:21:59,860 --> 00:22:00,970
I saw it just now.

428
00:22:02,380 --> 00:22:05,940
The last time this wedding dress killed someone

429
00:22:06,080 --> 00:22:07,080
was a few days ago.

430
00:22:07,700 --> 00:22:08,600
The person who died

431
00:22:08,600 --> 00:22:12,060
was the new bride of Guo Huo, the young master of Cailian Manor.

432
00:22:13,270 --> 00:22:14,440
I haven't asked you yet.

433
00:22:14,440 --> 00:22:15,540
Why did you suddenly ask me to investigate

434
00:22:15,540 --> 00:22:17,270
the cases about Cailian Manor?

435
00:22:17,700 --> 00:22:19,100
I'm looking for a person.

436
00:22:20,570 --> 00:22:21,870
His name is Shi Hun.

437
00:22:22,920 --> 00:22:24,050
As long as I find him,

438
00:22:24,210 --> 00:22:26,660
I can find the whereabouts of my other friend.

439
00:22:26,660 --> 00:22:27,610
The last time he was heard from

440
00:22:27,610 --> 00:22:29,700
was ten years ago in Cailian Manor.

441
00:22:30,320 --> 00:22:31,720
It was also ten years ago?

442
00:22:32,060 --> 00:22:33,330
Your friend appeared

443
00:22:33,350 --> 00:22:34,670
in Cailian Manor ten years ago.

444
00:22:34,670 --> 00:22:36,220
The first murder in Cailian Manor

445
00:22:36,220 --> 00:22:37,560
also happened ten years ago.

446
00:22:37,560 --> 00:22:38,690
What a coincidence!

447
00:22:39,150 --> 00:22:40,550
Is there any connection?

448
00:22:40,550 --> 00:22:41,810
Your analysis is good.

449
00:22:43,490 --> 00:22:45,100
There's a very high possibility.

450
00:22:45,100 --> 00:22:46,900
Three murders happened in a row.

451
00:22:47,190 --> 00:22:48,120
Detective Fang.

452
00:22:48,540 --> 00:22:50,930
You have to go to Cailian Manor.

453
00:22:52,020 --> 00:22:52,760
Cut it out.

454
00:22:53,860 --> 00:22:56,260
You just want me to help you look for people.

455
00:22:56,540 --> 00:22:57,800
I don't have time for that.

456
00:22:57,800 --> 00:22:59,800
I finally have clues to the whereabouts of Di Feisheng.

457
00:22:59,800 --> 00:23:00,800
I must find him.

458
00:23:01,680 --> 00:23:02,270
Fine.

459
00:23:02,460 --> 00:23:03,820
When I find Shi Hun,

460
00:23:04,020 --> 00:23:06,620
I'll help you ask him about the whereabouts of Di Feisheng.

461
00:23:06,620 --> 00:23:07,550
What do you mean?

462
00:23:07,780 --> 00:23:10,510
Because Shi Hun belongs to the Jinyuan Alliance.

463
00:23:10,770 --> 00:23:11,800
You did it on purpose, didn't you?

464
00:23:11,800 --> 00:23:12,930
Are you going or not?

465
00:23:14,620 --> 00:23:15,130
No.

466
00:23:19,240 --> 00:23:19,840
By the way,

467
00:23:20,970 --> 00:23:21,950
I bought some expensive medicine

468
00:23:21,950 --> 00:23:23,880
such as Cordyceps and tiger bones.

469
00:23:23,910 --> 00:23:25,840
Take it. It's good for your health.

470
00:23:26,450 --> 00:23:26,970
Wait.

471
00:23:31,630 --> 00:23:32,430
Fang Duobing.

472
00:23:32,750 --> 00:23:34,270
You're penniless.

473
00:23:34,600 --> 00:23:36,730
Where did you get the money to buy this?

474
00:23:38,550 --> 00:23:39,210
It's yours.

475
00:23:40,650 --> 00:23:41,390
Mine?

476
00:23:43,140 --> 00:23:44,340
Where did you find it?

477
00:23:44,820 --> 00:23:46,990
Your drawers, cabinets, and bedsides.

478
00:23:46,990 --> 00:23:47,370
Also,

479
00:23:47,730 --> 00:23:49,510
there was some money hidden under your rice jar.

480
00:23:49,510 --> 00:23:52,440
Aren't these the places where you hide your nest egg?

481
00:23:57,060 --> 00:23:57,560
Good.

482
00:23:58,310 --> 00:23:58,920
Very good.

483
00:24:00,260 --> 00:24:01,190
How can we go now?

484
00:24:01,920 --> 00:24:03,320
There's not a penny left.

485
00:24:03,350 --> 00:24:04,080
How can we go?

486
00:24:04,260 --> 00:24:04,710
No.

487
00:24:05,670 --> 00:24:06,770
That's all you hid?

488
00:24:07,860 --> 00:24:08,780
Where else could I hide?

489
00:24:08,780 --> 00:24:09,130
I...

490
00:24:15,530 --> 00:24:19,090
[Cailian Manor]

491
00:24:20,980 --> 00:24:24,050
[Mysterious Lotus Casebook]

492
00:24:30,830 --> 00:24:31,360
Go ahead.

493
00:24:34,700 --> 00:24:36,630
Do you still need travel expenses?

494
00:24:39,530 --> 00:24:40,790
Ladies and gentlemen.

495
00:24:40,820 --> 00:24:41,550
Come here.

496
00:24:41,740 --> 00:24:43,070
Here are vegetables for sale!

497
00:24:43,070 --> 00:24:44,210
Fresh vegetables!

498
00:24:44,890 --> 00:24:46,150
-Come and have a look.
-The vegetables are good.

499
00:24:46,150 --> 00:24:46,730
The vegetables are good.

500
00:24:46,730 --> 00:24:47,070
Yes.

501
00:24:47,380 --> 00:24:48,500
They're very fresh.

502
00:24:48,500 --> 00:24:49,670
Listen to me.

503
00:24:50,360 --> 00:24:51,110
These vegetables

504
00:24:51,110 --> 00:24:52,440
were just dug out of the ground.

505
00:24:52,440 --> 00:24:53,410
They're very fresh.

506
00:24:53,410 --> 00:24:54,270
Let me tell you.

507
00:24:54,350 --> 00:24:55,330
Most importantly,

508
00:24:55,330 --> 00:24:56,420
if you buy these vegetables,

509
00:24:56,420 --> 00:24:57,920
this young man will deliver them to your houses.

510
00:24:57,920 --> 00:24:58,830
-Deliver them?
-Really?

511
00:24:58,830 --> 00:24:59,230
You...

512
00:24:59,710 --> 00:25:00,420
So nice.

513
00:25:00,460 --> 00:25:01,360
Give it to me.

514
00:25:01,380 --> 00:25:01,930
Take your time.

515
00:25:01,930 --> 00:25:03,490
Take your time.

516
00:25:04,180 --> 00:25:04,910
Three taels.

517
00:25:05,190 --> 00:25:05,870
Perfect.

518
00:25:06,220 --> 00:25:07,100
Take your time.

519
00:25:08,390 --> 00:25:09,830
Li Lianhua, why did you leave?

520
00:25:09,830 --> 00:25:11,260
How much is half a kilo of vegetables?

521
00:25:11,260 --> 00:25:12,790
Why did you leave me behind?

522
00:25:13,270 --> 00:25:15,130
Everyone has a chance to buy them.

523
00:25:16,120 --> 00:25:17,230
My Lord.

524
00:25:18,380 --> 00:25:20,780
I want to know how to detoxify Bicha Poison.

525
00:25:21,100 --> 00:25:21,460
Yes.

526
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:22,560
Also,

527
00:25:23,810 --> 00:25:25,520
go and fish for information about the Tianji Hall's young master,

528
00:25:25,520 --> 00:25:26,430
Fang Duobing.

529
00:25:26,610 --> 00:25:27,940
It might be useful to me.

530
00:25:27,970 --> 00:25:30,770
Don't let Jiao Liqiao's people know these things.

531
00:25:30,830 --> 00:25:32,030
I'll do it right away.

532
00:25:39,900 --> 00:25:40,830
Why are you here?

533
00:25:42,980 --> 00:25:44,180
Who was that just now?

534
00:25:45,480 --> 00:25:46,070
Stop!

535
00:25:47,550 --> 00:25:48,810
Li Lianhua is not here.

536
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:50,730
I have something to ask you.

537
00:25:51,980 --> 00:25:53,410
Why did you hit him today?

538
00:25:56,580 --> 00:25:57,440
Say something.

539
00:25:57,730 --> 00:25:59,520
I know you are not Iron Head Slave.

540
00:25:59,520 --> 00:26:00,520
So I want to ask you

541
00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:02,630
why you approached us.

542
00:26:03,010 --> 00:26:05,210
What makes you think you have something

543
00:26:05,360 --> 00:26:06,710
that is worthy of approach?

544
00:26:06,710 --> 00:26:07,110
You...

545
00:26:09,140 --> 00:26:10,670
You are here for Li Lianhua.

546
00:26:12,170 --> 00:26:13,900
Do you think I came here for you?

547
00:26:16,230 --> 00:26:16,830
Forget it.

548
00:26:17,690 --> 00:26:18,620
I don't argue with people

549
00:26:18,620 --> 00:26:20,150
who're not good at martial arts.

550
00:26:20,150 --> 00:26:21,610
I don't want to talk to you.

551
00:26:33,750 --> 00:26:34,810
I'm a man of my word.

552
00:26:35,330 --> 00:26:37,190
I'll let you battle with me again.

553
00:26:39,700 --> 00:26:42,180
The last place Shi Hun appeared is Cailian Manor.

554
00:26:42,180 --> 00:26:43,400
I'll go there with you.

555
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:45,460
When you find the corpse of Shan Gudao,

556
00:26:45,460 --> 00:26:46,990
don't forget your promise.

557
00:26:50,900 --> 00:26:51,940
He's so stubborn.

558
00:27:03,530 --> 00:27:04,190
Li Lianhua.

559
00:27:05,390 --> 00:27:06,720
Let me tell you a secret.

560
00:27:07,700 --> 00:27:08,410
Fei

561
00:27:09,080 --> 00:27:10,960
met someone secretly yesterday.

562
00:27:11,240 --> 00:27:12,840
I also followed that person.

563
00:27:12,940 --> 00:27:15,070
Unfortunately, that person ran away.

