00:39:02,610 --> 00:39:03,900
This is the best place to admire the lotuses.

842
00:39:03,900 --> 00:39:04,500
Thank you.

843
00:39:13,740 --> 00:39:15,270
This is indeed a good place.

844
00:39:15,420 --> 00:39:16,550
It's such a big pond.

845
00:39:16,580 --> 00:39:18,450
We might be able to even catch fishes here.

846
00:39:18,450 --> 00:39:20,250
It's useless for you to be anxious.

847
00:39:20,250 --> 00:39:22,440
What if Master Guo hides something deliberately?

848
00:39:22,440 --> 00:39:24,440
If you ask him now, you'll alert him.

849
00:39:24,580 --> 00:39:25,380
Why don't you

850
00:39:25,400 --> 00:39:27,010
investigate the case about Cailian Manor

851
00:39:27,010 --> 00:39:28,910
and find out what happened ten years ago?

852
00:39:28,910 --> 00:39:30,570
Maybe there will be new clues.

853
00:39:31,810 --> 00:39:34,610
You still want me to help you investigate the case.

854
00:39:35,270 --> 00:39:35,870
It's easy.

855
00:39:36,330 --> 00:39:38,290
I'll go and torture Guo Qian.

856
00:39:39,060 --> 00:39:39,580
Fei.

857
00:39:39,780 --> 00:39:40,650
Don't act recklessly.

858
00:39:40,650 --> 00:39:41,520
Fang Duobing, don't chase him.

859
00:39:41,520 --> 00:39:42,120
Let him go.

860
00:39:43,050 --> 00:39:44,340
He has no experience in investigating cases.

861
00:39:44,340 --> 00:39:45,390
He's also violent.

862
00:39:45,390 --> 00:39:46,740
If he gets angry and hits others,

863
00:39:46,740 --> 00:39:47,160
then...

864
00:39:47,160 --> 00:39:48,320
He won't. Don't worry.

865
00:39:48,320 --> 00:39:49,360
He's an adult.

866
00:39:52,380 --> 00:39:53,050
Li Lianhua.

867
00:39:53,690 --> 00:39:55,460
I'm becoming more and more curious.

868
00:39:55,460 --> 00:39:56,920
Do you trust him that much?

869
00:39:57,480 --> 00:39:58,190
Trust?

870
00:40:00,640 --> 00:40:02,350
The deceased hasn't been buried yet.

871
00:40:02,350 --> 00:40:04,140
Why don't we go to the mourning hall and burn incense sticks for her?

872
00:40:04,140 --> 00:40:04,490
Let's go.

873
00:40:04,490 --> 00:40:04,890
You...

874
00:40:11,020 --> 00:40:12,330
The coffin should be kept here for seven days.

875
00:40:12,330 --> 00:40:14,260
Only three days passed, but no one is here now.

876
00:40:14,260 --> 00:40:16,450
People of Cailian Manor really don't care about

877
00:40:16,450 --> 00:40:18,180
this young madam who just died.

878
00:40:24,380 --> 00:40:24,900
Look.

879
00:40:25,160 --> 00:40:25,980
Abdominal distension.

880
00:40:25,980 --> 00:40:27,040
There's water inside.

881
00:40:27,040 --> 00:40:28,700
It does look like she drowned.

882
00:40:28,790 --> 00:40:29,920
The body is swollen.

883
00:40:30,110 --> 00:40:31,440
The spots are light red.

884
00:40:31,620 --> 00:40:33,960
It does look like the spots appeared slowly

885
00:40:33,960 --> 00:40:36,080
because the body was soaked before.

886
00:40:37,140 --> 00:40:39,220
She has a lot of bruises on her neck.

887
00:40:43,850 --> 00:40:44,920
What are you doing?

888
00:40:46,120 --> 00:40:47,120
Young Master Guo.

889
00:40:47,170 --> 00:40:48,930
There's still something fishy about your wife's death.

890
00:40:48,930 --> 00:40:50,260
We want to check it again

891
00:40:50,390 --> 00:40:52,230
to bring justice to the deceased.

892
00:40:52,230 --> 00:40:54,220
What should be checked has already been checked.

893
00:40:54,220 --> 00:40:55,270
She has already passed away.

894
00:40:55,270 --> 00:40:57,270
Please don't disturb the deceased.

895
00:40:57,940 --> 00:40:58,780
Young Master Guo.

896
00:40:58,780 --> 00:40:59,660
To be honest,

897
00:41:00,110 --> 00:41:02,120
your wife appeared in my dream a few days ago.

898
00:41:02,120 --> 00:41:03,150
She cried and expressed her grievances.

899
00:41:03,150 --> 00:41:04,290
She said she couldn't rest in peace.

900
00:41:04,290 --> 00:41:06,020
That's why we came to Cailian Manor.

901
00:41:06,020 --> 00:41:07,550
She appeared in your dream?

902
00:41:08,550 --> 00:41:10,410
This is the master of Lotus Tower.

903
00:41:10,560 --> 00:41:12,220
People call him Physician Li.

904
00:41:12,390 --> 00:41:13,340
He's psychic.

905
00:41:13,730 --> 00:41:15,260
His dreams are believable.

906
00:41:16,310 --> 00:41:17,230
Even so,

907
00:41:17,670 --> 00:41:19,270
I should tell my father first

908
00:41:19,520 --> 00:41:21,070
and get his permission.

909
00:41:21,290 --> 00:41:23,220
You seem to be afraid of Master Guo.

910
00:41:23,280 --> 00:41:25,890
It's right and proper that children obey their fathers' orders.

911
00:41:25,890 --> 00:41:26,890
Young Master Guo.

912
00:41:27,270 --> 00:41:28,920
Now that the coffin has been opened,

913
00:41:28,920 --> 00:41:30,580
she's already been offended.

914
00:41:30,750 --> 00:41:32,700
I'll apologize to Master Guo later.

915
00:41:32,700 --> 00:41:33,960
If he really blames us,

916
00:41:34,230 --> 00:41:36,030
I'll take full responsibility.

917
00:41:39,080 --> 00:41:41,230
This body didn't just have superficial injuries.

918
00:41:41,230 --> 00:41:43,070
Her carpal bones were fractured.

919
00:41:43,070 --> 00:41:45,670
Her cervical spine was also severely damaged.

920
00:41:46,350 --> 00:41:47,920
We never hit her.

921
00:41:48,220 --> 00:41:50,340
The people from the government have already investigated before.

922
00:41:50,340 --> 00:41:52,500
They said the bride fell into the water by accident

923
00:41:52,500 --> 00:41:54,750
and that the injuries were caused when she struggled.

924
00:41:54,750 --> 00:41:56,860
It doesn't seem like she was beaten up.

925
00:41:56,860 --> 00:41:57,860
Young Master Guo.

926
00:41:58,300 --> 00:42:00,700
Did anything happen before the bride died?

927
00:42:02,590 --> 00:42:04,230
There was nothing special.

928
00:42:05,930 --> 00:42:07,650
After she had dinner that night,

929
00:42:07,650 --> 00:42:09,310
Su went back to our room alone.

930
00:42:09,310 --> 00:42:12,240
She said she wanted to try on the wedding dress again.

931
00:42:20,700 --> 00:42:22,070
No one knows what happened

932
00:42:22,070 --> 00:42:23,710
after the bride went back to the room?

